    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the robust Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through an M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed cooling system including a high-flow water pump. Recent maintenance includes a valve clearance adjustment and rod bearing inspection to ensure the high-revving internals remain within factory tolerances. Riding on staggered Style 67 wheels with Michelin Pilot Sport rubber, this M3 offers precise turn-in and exceptional mechanical grip. A mechanically sound enthusiast's choice ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
