    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and refined performance. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish with only the minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the body panels remain straight and well-aligned. Inside, the cabin has been meticulously preserved; the upholstery is clean and supple, and every electronic component\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in robust health, benefiting from a comprehensive service history and a recent professional inspection. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires provide excellent grip with significant tread life remaining. Garage-kept and smoke-free, this car represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine pride of ownership.",
